PrecisEnactment of the CORRECTED CERTIFICATES REMISSION ORDER which provides for the remission of fees and interest charges payable by any corporation to whom a corrected certificate was issued pursuant to subsection 265(1) of the Canada Business Corporations Act between October 3, 1991 and June 8, 1992, where those fees and charges have not yet been paid.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1998-0090 Publication Date: 1998-09-16
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the CORRECTED CERTIFICATES REMISSION ORDER which provides for
the remission of fees and interest charges payable by any corporation to
whom a corrected certificate was issued pursuant to subsection 265(1) of
the Canada Business Corporations Act between October 3, 1991 and June 8,
1992, where those fees and charges have not yet been paid.
